For Day 1 puzzle,while dialling in from 50 with subsequent left and right rotation 0 comes at frequent interval for 3 times.Here,both Java's String method and Kotlin's atomic String method can be run.
For Day 3 puzzle,Kotlin function will call each integer having the highest voltage value and compare each subsequent integer value with comparitively highest value 
For Day 4 puzzle,each piece of paper needs to be carried by a forklift when there will be less than 4 papers near the wall.A newer forklift carries as much paper to give a clearer path.Interconnected GCP Cloud Shell K8S node with parallel Java Maven API can give a fast response with each IAM runnable with Jetbrains IDE.
